text:
Saini bhaiiiiiiiii
Tere liye dil se respect nikalti hain. Mujhe aaj bhi Pizza Hut vala lunch yaad hain jab hum pehli baar campus se ghar jaa rhe they midsem break ke liye. Station pe bhi kaafi der tak tere sath bakchodi kari jab teri train late hogayi thi, tabse tere sath ek connection ban gaya tha. 
Campus main chaapu banna bohot log sikhate hain, but tunhe ek accha insaan banna sikhaya, jo shayad puri life sath rahega. 

Milte rahenge, UPSC ke liye best of luck <3
author: Tushar  Goswamy

text:
Bro pura second year tere bharose pass kiya hain maine XD
Jab bhi koi doubt hota tha tere room bhag ke chale jaata tha, bina soche ki tunhe woh course kiya hain ki nahi. Mujhe pura confidence tha ki tu sahi rasta dikhayega, and tunhe har course main bohot zyada help ki. Thank you so much, bhai, for always being there for me and helping me with the silliest doubts. 

Love you lots bhai, and thank you soooooo much.
Zyada bengali aati nahi, but Tomake Bhalobasi bhai <3
author: Tushar  Goswamy

text:
From that nightout in the library before Poddar ka endsem, to flying Laudasur on the airstrip, I can't imagine surviving aero without you. Bhai teri vajeh se I felt lucky and blessed to have got a branch change in Aero. CPI jaisi bhi aayi, but AE main maaze bohot zyada aaye thanks to you. Last day jab tu room aaya tab kaafi emotional hogaya tha, isiliye bol nahi paaya, but will miss you a lot. 
I have passed most of my AE courses thanks to you, graduation credits main sabse upar tera naam ayega XD.
Milte rahenge, apna US trip ka plan abhi bhi On hain. Plus Chennai se to tera ghar zyada dur nahi :-P

Ni A*** Denge
author: Tushar  Goswamy

Bas yahi umeed rahegi ki job main bhi tere jaisa hi koi roommate mil jaye flat share karne ke liye.

D316 for life <3
